Requirements Specification
==========================

Overview
--------

The intent is to have a system to allow competitors/timekeepers to have quick access to all times and positions in the event.  The system should also allow non-technical timekeepers to enter data in a quick an efficient manner with the ability to alter times in the event of a mistake.  This should be displayed on TV/monitor screens and also have the ability for competitors to access the same information on a mobile device.

Timekeepers/Officials
---------------------

Configure an event to define specific parameters:
    - Name of event
    - Date of event
    - Number of courses
    - Number of runs per course
    - Competitor No.
    - Competitor Name
    - Class Entered

Option to import the above data from a spreadsheet - this will allow

Enter times per competitor
